Charity.Mission: The Grandparent Autism Network, an all-volunteer, international nonprofit organization, supports grandparents of children with autism.  GAN's mission is to promote awareness and understanding of autism and to enhance the resources essential to community responsiveness.  Two websites, www.ganinfo.org and www.faninfo.org, provide information, programs and projects to improve the quality of life for families.  Networking together, grandparents are a vital resource for autism - and each other!
